pic Weapon Attained: Orb of Mastery</font></a><br><img src="http://209.164.24.44/eqlore/images/pages_links_box.gif"><font face="verdana" size="1">&nbsp;<a href="#12">[12/5/2000]&nbsp;&nbsp;Twelve Days of Velious Day Eleven</font></a><br><img src="http://209.164.24.44/eqlore/images/pages_links_box.gif"><font face="verdana" size="1">&nbsp;<a href="#13">[12/5/2000]&nbsp;&nbsp;MMORPG Digest Issue # 2</font></a><br><img src="http://209.164.24.44/eqlore/images/pages_links_box.gif"><font face="verdana" size="1">&nbsp;<a href="#14">[12/5/2000]&nbsp;&nbsp;Guildsay.com opens it's doors</font></a><br><img src="http://209.164.24.44/eqlore/images/pages_links_box.gif"><font face="verdana" size="1">&nbsp;<a href="#15">[12/5/2000]&nbsp;&nbsp;Luclin: The Stryngs of Ayre Tournament</font></a><br><img src="http://209.164.24.44/eqlore/images/pages_links_box.gif"><font face="verdana" size="1">&nbsp;<a href="#16">[12/4/2000]&nbsp;&nbsp;<B>More exclusive Scars of Velious shots!</B></font></a><br><img src="http://209.164.24.44/eqlore/images/pages_links_box.gif"><font face="verdana" size="1">&nbsp;<a href="#17">[12/4/2000]&nbsp;&nbsp;The Scars of Velious ships to stores!</font></a><br><img src="http://209.164.24.44/eqlore/images/pages_links_box.gif"><font face="verdana" size="1">&nbsp;<a href="#18">[12/4/2000]&nbsp;&nbsp;Brad McQuaid on Scars shipping</font></a><br><img src="http://209.164.24.44/eqlore/images/pages_links_box.gif"><font face="verdana" size="1">&nbsp;<a href="#19">[12/4/2000]&nbsp;&nbsp;Emergency downtime early tomorrow</font></a><br><img src="http://209.164.24.44/eqlore/images/pages_links_box.gif"><font face="verdana" size="1">&nbsp;<a href="#20">[12/4/2000]&nbsp;&nbsp;Monday evening comments from Alan</font></a><br>
